text: My daughter needs structure and a routine in her life so needs to do school work and happily gets on with it. My son is a monkey. He keeps sneaking back to Netflix and battles all work! They are with their Dad today so I am playing catch up. Running is my re-set. I am doing too much of it. Should be taking the opportunity to rest...
Sad that you are coming to the end... but exciting that there is a new beginning!!
